readable.content: A skier in a yellow jacket is airborne above the mountains . A skier jumps high in the air with a view of the mountains . A skiing man in a fluorescent jacket jumps very high and it looks as though he is flying . Somone is high in the air doing a ski jump . The skier in the green jacket and white pants appears to almost fly into the sky .
